name: Lalla Aicha (Aïsha Qandisha)
shortLoreBlurb: Lalla Aicha (Aïsha Qandisha) is a spirit from Morocco/Maghreb associated with seduction, water. Appeased for safe passage and rains.
overlapsLinks: Manannán (Celtic), Naga (India/SE Asia), Poseidon (Greek), Tangaroa (Polynesia), Yemaya (Yoruba)
